Description: Adjust Wine DLL search paths for Winlator/GameNative rootfs layout.
             Winlator mounts its Wine rootfs at a non-standard location, so Wine's
             built-in path resolution needs to be aware of it.
Author: Derived from brunodev85/wine-9.2-custom
Origin: https://github.com/brunodev85/wine-9.2-custom

NOTE: This patch file is intentionally left as a template/placeholder.
      The actual patch content should be extracted by diffing
      brunodev85/wine-9.2-custom against its base Wine version:

        git clone https://github.com/brunodev85/wine-9.2-custom winlator-wine
        git clone https://gitlab.winehq.org/wine/wine.git upstream-wine
        cd upstream-wine
        git diff wine-9.2 ../winlator-wine > ../patches/001-winlator-paths.patch

      This is done automatically by the CI if PATCH_SOURCE=winlator is set
      in build-wine.yml. For manual builds, generate the patch file yourself
      using the commands above before running build-wine.sh.

To regenerate patches automatically from the Winlator fork:
  scripts/generate-patches.sh winlator
